description: Returns the timestamp and status of the last cache reset of a specific Amazon Lightsail content delivery network (CDN) distribution.

parameters.name: distributionName
parameters.description: The name of the distribution for which to return the timestamp of the last cache reset. Use the GetDistributions action to get a list of distribution names that you can specify. When omitted, the response includes the latest cache reset timestamp of all your distributions.

nested_items.name: status
nested_items.description: The status of the last cache reset.

nested_items.name: createTime
nested_items.description: The timestamp of the last cache reset ( 1479734909.17) in Unix time format.
